Hi everyone we are using the new way to send recording like shown here <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/crm/extensions/recordings-and-transcriptions>
```request object ===>
{
    "url": "<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/extensions/calling/1300130/settings/recording>",
    "headers": {
        "authorization": "Bearer <<private access token>>",
        "content-type": "application/json"
    },
    "body": {
        "urlToRetrieveAuthedRecording": "<https://localhost:8000/integrations/HubSpot/recordings/%s>"
    },
    "json": true
}
response we got back ===>
{
    "status": "error",
    "message": "This API can't be called using an OAuth access token. A valid developer API key must be provided in the `hapikey` query parameter, and a valid `appId` must be provided in the API request.",
    "correlationId": "503ce754-95cd-4f61-bd0d-a7f576adbd4a",
    "links": {
        "docs": "<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/developer-tools-overview#developer-api-keys>"
    },
    "category": "INVALID_AUTHENTICATION"
}```

